---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={`About — ${SITE_TITLE}`} description="Jack Maguire is a performance marketing and paid social media director based in East Village, NYC. 12+ years managing paid social campaigns across Meta, TikTok, and Instagram." />
		<script type="application/ld+json">
		{
			"@context": "https://schema.org",
			"@type": "Person",
			"name": "Jack Maguire",
			"url": "https://jackmaguire.org",
			"jobTitle": "Paid Social Media Director",
			"alumniOf": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "McGill University" },
			"address": { "@type": "PostalAddress", "addressLocality": "New York", "addressRegion": "NY" },
			"sameAs": ["https://www.linkedin.com/in/paidsocialdirector/"]
		}
		</script>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>About</h1>
			<div class="prose">
				<p>
					I'm Jack Maguire. I live in the East Village in New York City. I've spent 12+ years
					working in performance marketing and paid social media — starting from nothing in particular
					and building up to director-level roles managing large-scale advertising programs across
					Meta, TikTok, Instagram, Facebook, and Snapchat. This site is where I write about what
					I'm paying attention to: NYC food, travel, philosophy, AI, and occasionally work.
				</p>

				<h2>Work</h2>
				<p>
					I'm a paid social media director and performance marketing specialist. Most recently
					I was Senior Paid Social Media Director at National Debt Relief (March 2022 – January
					2026), where I managed over $1M in monthly ad spend across Meta and TikTok, led a team
					of paid social managers, and worked closely with legal and compliance on advertising in
					the regulated debt settlement industry.
				</p>
				<p>
					Before that: Good Apple (NYC agency, paid social strategy), Visiting Angels (managed
					paid social across 800+ franchise locations), Ascension Press (grew Facebook and YouTube
					to 100K+ followers), and Renegade Communications (media buying and campaign management).
					My platforms have included Meta, TikTok, Instagram, Facebook, Snapchat, Pinterest,
					LinkedIn, Reddit, Quora, and YouTube.
				</p>
				<p>
					I've been an AI-first practitioner for several years — using LLMs daily for campaign
					optimization, creative briefing, and analytics work since well before it became common
					practice. I think a lot about how AI is actually changing performance marketing, not
					the hype version.
				</p>

				<h2>This site</h2>
				<p>
					I write about what I'm genuinely interested in. That means NYC food and restaurants
					(food is my primary lens for exploring a city — I'll visit 25+ places in a single trip
					before I visit a single museum). It means travel, with a preference for building real
					itineraries rather than following someone else's. It means philosophy, which I studied
					at McGill and have never really stopped thinking about. It means AI tools in practice,
					not in theory. And it means the occasional essay on whatever I can't stop turning over.
				</p>

				<h2>Outside work</h2>
				<p>
					Before my junior year of college I thru-hiked the Appalachian Trail — 2,178 miles in
					99 days with my brother. That's still the hardest thing I've done and the experience
					I return to most when I need to remember I can figure things out. I've run three
					marathons. I've read somewhere north of 300 books, with a bias toward systems thinking,
					behavioral economics, philosophy, theology, and narrative history. I moved to New York
					City because the city feeds something real — I live in the East Village and try not
					to take it for granted.
				</p>

				<h2>Background</h2>
				<ul>
					<li>Most recently: Senior Paid Social Media Director, National Debt Relief</li>
					<li>Previously: Good Apple &middot; Visiting Angels &middot; Ascension Press &middot; Renegade Communications</li>
					<li>McGill University — Business Management &amp; Philosophy</li>
					<li>East Village, New York City</li>
				</ul>

				<h2>Contact</h2>
				<p>
					Email: <a href="mailto:maguirebaseball@gmail.com">maguirebaseball@gmail.com</a>
				</p>
			</div>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	.prose {
		max-width: 600px;
	}
	.prose h2 {
		font-size: 1.2em;
		margin-top: 2em;
		margin-bottom: 0.5em;
	}
	.prose ul {
		padding-left: 1.5em;
	}
	.prose li {
		margin-bottom: 0.3em;
	}
</style>
